lead_paragraph: Manchester United have been rejuvenated under new manager Jose Mourinho and are poised to mount a strong challenge for the Premier League title, skipper Wayne Rooney has said.

headline.print_headline: Rooney Expects Rejuvenated Man Utd to Challenge for Title
